name: #distorted SCAMMER OFFERED ME $1500 FOR AN NFT
description:
Scammer willing to pay me $1500 for a job, here the full conversation:

We are ready to buy from you NFTs that you create specifically for us. At this stage we have an alpha version of the game and an official website of our team where you can find out more information. What do you think?🔥
ME:Hey cool, i like the idea
SCAMMER:We need a character that is similar to the one in the main menu, you need to look at him in motion and understand his character. You can download the game on our website RelaGames.com by entering the invite PXG289-7421B2
And see what you can think of.
ME:Ok let me check it out
SCAMMER:ok and ?
ME:Yeah... Wait a few more minutes please
ME:How much i will be paid?
SCAMMER:We are ready to pay up to $ 1500 Depends on the quality of your work
ME:I would like to be paid in Tezos, could it be possible? 🤔
SCAMMER:okay
ME:*THE ROCK SMILING GIF*
